## Method to write the sum of two integer numbers
## The integer class receives integer numbers
_method integer.method_sum(n2)
## The method as_integer() converts string to integer
sum << _self.as_integer() + n2
## The method write_string converts integer to string 
sum_string << sum.write_string

write( "The sum is " + sum_string )
    _return 
_endmethod